  "title": "Operations Support Officer",
  "description": "<h3>Job Responsibilities</h3><p>Front Office<br />* Manage day to day operations tasks liaising with Back Office<br />* To provide cargo and shipping operations support to LPG and Crude & Products Teams.<br />* To ensure risks and exposures are highlighted for all sales and purchase agreements and are issued timely, accurately and updated in systems.<br />* To analyse trading exposure and profit / loss.<br />* To make necessary external and internal reporting documents in English and Japanese for close communication with Japan HQ.<br /><br />Back Office<br />* To support in budgeting control and accounting analysis for PL, BS, CF.<br />* To support in working capital control (daily / monthly / quarterly / yearly).<br /></p><h3>Job Requirements</h3><p>* More than 3 years of LPG and Crude & Products Trading / Operations / Risk Analysis experience.<br />* Good written and spoken Japanese is required for close communication with Tokyo HQ Team.<br /></p>",
